  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (205°C).",
    "Season the fish with salt and pepper.",
    "Place the fish in a baking dish, skin side up. Arrange tomatoes around them.",
    "In a small bowl, mix minced garlic, olive oil, lemon juice, and chopped parsley. Drizzle this mixture over the fish and tomatoes.",
